title: Top Google Searched Questions Answered by Curl Expert | Christin Brown
itunes:title: Top Google Searched Questions Answered by Curl Expert | Christin Brown
description:
This is our one-year podcast anniversary! It's been such a great journey. I'm so grateful to all of you.

Today, we have Christin Brown, aka the Curl Factor. She is one of the foremost experts in curls. In this episode, we are going to answer your top searched curly hair questions.
